/*
Key of pin operations:
DDR:           0=input, 1=output
input PORT:    0=disable pullup, 1=enable pullup
output PORT:   0=drive low, 1=drive high
write to PIN:  1=toggle value of PORT
read from PIN: value on the pin


Initializations:
DDRD4 = 0 - BTN1 input
PORT4 = 1 - BTN1 pullup

DDRG0 = X - NC
DDRG1 = X - NC
DDRG2 = 1 - LED (output)
DDRG3 = ? - Q2 Oscillator
DDRG4 = ? - Q2 Oscillator
*/

